
	Package Development
	
	React	-	Reusable components
	
	composer	-	dependency manager for PHP
	
	npm
	
	nuget
	
	composer require
	
	Package:	An independent module that can coupled in various 
				projects
				
	Why packages:
		1. Re-usability
		2. Independent of business logic of a particular project
		
		
		
		pramanit
		onlits account	-	single sign-on to multiple services
		
		Waterfall model
		
		accounting
		inventory
		payroll
		
	Pre-requisite:
		1. Loose-coupling
		2. Test Driven Development (TDD)
		
		
	
